{"_id":"2f42bb65bfbf401b","name":"Channel Divinity","type":"action","img":"icons/skills/melee/blade-damage.webp","system":{"description":"Divine Gift Trait\n- **Range:** 30-foot radius centered on you\n- **Effect:** Automatically succeeds for Heal/Harm intents (see Part 7 for full details)\n- **Types:** Heal, Harm, Turn (undead), Command (undead)\n- **Energy Cost:** Minimum 4 Energy, can spend more\n- **Notes:**\n  - Counts as ONE combat action for Multiple Action Penalty purposes\n  - Indiscriminate area effect (affects friends and foes)\n  - See (Magic System) for Channel Divinity details\n\n### Combat Maneuvers\n\nThese maneuvers modify or replace your standard attacks:","actionType":"combat","actionCost":"2 [Combat] actions","trigger":"","effect":"Automatically succeeds for Heal/Harm intents (see Part 7 for full details)\n- **Types:** Heal, Harm, Turn (undead), Command (undead)\n- **Energy Cost:** Minimum 4 Energy, can spend more\n- **Notes:**\n  - Counts as ONE combat action for Multiple Action Penalty purposes\n  - Indiscriminate area effect (affects friends and foes)\n  - See (Magic System) for Channel Divinity details\n\n### Combat Maneuvers\n\nThese maneuvers modify or replace your standard attacks:","keywords":[],"range":"30-foot radius centered on you","target":"","frequency":"","special":""},"effects":[]}
