{"_id":"b6ad1ebf69244788","name":"Melee Attack","type":"action","img":"icons/skills/melee/blade-damage.webp","system":{"description":"Target must be within your melee reach (typically 5 feet)\n- **Effect:** Make an opposed attack roll (Agility + Melee Combat vs opponent's Agility + Melee Combat)\n- **Damage on Success:**\n  - Margin 0 (Tie): Defender wins, no damage\n  - Margin 1: Base weapon damage\n  - Margin 2+: Base weapon damage + Strength modifier\n- **Notes:**\n  - Uses Agility + Melee Combat skill\n  - Subject to Multiple Action Penalty\n  - Can be modified by combat maneuvers (see below)","actionType":"combat","actionCost":"1 [Combat] action","trigger":"","effect":"Make an opposed attack roll (Agility + Melee Combat vs opponent's Agility + Melee Combat)\n- **Damage on Success:**\n  - Margin 0 (Tie): Defender wins, no damage\n  - Margin 1: Base weapon damage\n  - Margin 2+: Base weapon damage + Strength modifier\n- **Notes:**\n  - Uses Agility + Melee Combat skill\n  - Subject to Multiple Action Penalty\n  - Can be modified by combat maneuvers (see below)","keywords":[],"range":"","target":"","frequency":"","special":""},"effects":[]}
